---

<div id="age-verification-overlay" class="age-overlay">
  <!-- Modal de verificaci√≥n -->
  <div id="age-modal" class="age-modal">
    <div class="age-icon">üîû</div>
    <p class="age-title">Verificaci√≥n de edad</p>
    <p>Este sitio web contiene informaci√≥n sobre apuestas deportivas. Debes ser mayor de <strong>18 a√±os</strong> para acceder.</p>
    <p class="age-question">¬øEres mayor de 18 a√±os?</p>
    <div class="age-buttons">
      <button id="age-yes" class="age-btn age-btn-yes">S√≠, soy mayor de 18</button>
      <button id="age-no" class="age-btn age-btn-no">No, soy menor de 18</button>
    </div>
    <p class="age-legal">El juego puede ser adictivo. Juega con responsabilidad.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Landing de acceso denegado -->
  <div id="age-denied" class="age-modal age-denied hidden">
    <div class="age-icon">‚õî</div>
    <p class="age-title">Acceso restringido</p>
    <p>Lo sentimos, no puedes acceder a este sitio web porque es necesario ser <strong>mayor de 18 a√±os</strong>.</p>
    <p>En Espa√±a, la legislaci√≥n vigente proh√≠be el acceso a contenidos relacionados con apuestas y juegos de azar a menores de edad.</p>
    <div class="denied-info">
      <p class="ayuda">Si necesitas ayuda</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>FEJAR:</strong> 900 200 225</li>
        <li><strong>RGIAJ:</strong> <a href="https://www.ordenacionjuego.es/participantes-juego/juego-seguro/rgiaj" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Autoprohibici√≥n</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <button id="age-back" class="age-btn age-btn-back">Volver a verificar</button>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .age-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    z-index: 10000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .age-title {
    font-size: calc(2rem + 0.5vw + 0.5vh) !important;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .ayuda {
    font-size: 0.9rem !important;
    color: #ffc107 !important;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .age-overlay.hidden,
  .age-modal.hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  .age-modal {
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    animation: modalAppear 0.3s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes modalAppear {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: scale(0.9) translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: scale(1) translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .age-icon {
    font-size: 64px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .age-modal h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffc107;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .age-modal p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #ccc;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .age-question {
    font-size: 1.1rem !important;
    color: #fff !important;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-top: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px !important;
  }

  .age-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .age-btn {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
  }

  .age-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .age-btn-yes {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffc107, #ff9800);
    color: #000;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.3);
  }

  .age-btn-yes:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.5);
  }

  .age-btn-no {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: #ccc;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .age-btn-no:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  .age-legal {
    font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    color: #888 !important;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Landing de acceso denegado */
  .age-denied.hidden {
    display: none;
  }

  .age-denied h2 {
    color: #e74c3c;
  }

  .denied-info {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .denied-info h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #ffc107;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .denied-info ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .denied-info li {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #aaa;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .age-btn-back {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    color: #ccc;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .age-btn-back:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .age-modal {
      padding: 28px 20px;
    }

    .age-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .age-icon {
      font-size: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  const overlay = document.getElementById('age-verification-overlay');
  const modal = document.getElementById('age-modal');
  const denied = document.getElementById('age-denied');
  const btnYes = document.getElementById('age-yes');
  const btnNo = document.getElementById('age-no');
  const btnBack = document.getElementById('age-back');

  // Comprobar si ya verific√≥ la edad
  if (localStorage.getItem('age_verified') === 'true') {
    overlay?.classList.add('hidden');
  } else {
    document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
  }

  btnYes?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    localStorage.setItem('age_verified', 'true');
    overlay?.classList.add('hidden');
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
  });

  btnNo?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    modal?.classList.add('hidden');
    denied?.classList.remove('hidden');
  });

  btnBack?.addEventListener('click', () => {
    denied?.classList.add('hidden');
    modal?.classList.remove('hidden');
  });
</script>
